        "text": "Seals are semi-aquatic carnivorous mammals found on beaches across Golarion. They're known for their extraordinary hunting skills, using their sensitive whiskers to detect the movement and the size of fish they're hunting, even allowing them to locate hidden prey",
        "type": "monster_family"
      },
